== 發行 ==
由[[二十世紀福斯|二十世紀福斯]]定於2015年5月22日在美國發行<ref name=May22nd-2015>{{cite news|last=Ford|first=Rebecca|title=Fox Shifts 'Fantastic Four' Reboot to Summer 2015, Dates Paul Feig's 'Susan Cooper'|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/fox-shifts-fantastic-four-reboot-655306|accessdate=21 February 2014|newspaper=hollywoodreporter.com|date=12 November 2013|archive-date=2014-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140722142850/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/fox-shifts-fantastic-four-reboot-655306|dead-url=no}}</ref>。後來在2015年3月，日期被移至2015年6月5日，這原先為《{{link-en|捉鬼事務所|B.O.O.: Bureau of Otherworldly Operations}}》和《[[紙上城市_(電影)|紙上城市]]》的上映日<ref>{{cite news|last1=Lesnick|first1=Silas|title=20th Century Fox Shifts Dates for Spy, Poltergeist and Paper Towns|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/416235-20th-century-fox-swaps-shifts-dates-for-spy-poltergeist-and-paper-towns|accessdate=March 9, 2015|publisher=comingsoon.net|date=March 4, 2015|archive-date=2018-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612181724/http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/416235-20th-century-fox-swaps-shifts-dates-for-spy-poltergeist-and-paper-towns|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在澳大利亞，電影提前於2015年5月21日釋出<ref>{{cite news|url=http://yourmovies.com.au/movie/47559/spy|accessdate=May 20, 2015|publisher=yourmovies.com.au|date=May 20, 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150521110853/http://yourmovies.com.au/movie/47559/spy|archivedate=2015年5月21日|title=存档副本}}</ref>。

=== 評價 ===
電影獲得了正面的評價，許多影評人稱讚[[梅丽莎·麦卡西|麥卡錫]]的主演表現和[[傑森史塔森|史塔森]]令人驚喜的喜劇角色<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2015/03/17/melissa-mccarthy-s-best-role-yet-from-bridesmaids-to-ass-kicking-cia-spy.html|title=Melissa McCarthy’s Best Role Yet: From 'Bridesmaids' to Ass-Kicking CIA 'Spy'|work=The Daily Beast|accessdate=19 March 2015|archive-date=2017-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170517103111/http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2015/03/17/melissa-mccarthy-s-best-role-yet-from-bridesmaids-to-ass-kicking-cia-spy.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2015/film/reviews/sxsw-film-review-melissa-mccarthy-in-spy-1201453420/|title=‘Spy’ Review: A Brilliant Showcase for Melissa McCarthy - Variety|author=Justin Chang|work=Variety|accessdate=19 March 2015|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108185633/https://variety.com/2015/film/reviews/sxsw-film-review-melissa-mccarthy-in-spy-1201453420/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]根據227位專業影評人持有94%的新鮮度，平均得分7.2／10<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/spy_2015/ |title=Spy |publisher=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2015-05-21 |archive-date=2021-03-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210318113205/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/spy_2015 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分75（滿分100），[[IMDB|IMDB]]得分7.1(滿分10)，正面評價居多<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/spy|title=Spy Reviews|work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]]|accessdate=March 17, 2015|archive-date=2018-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180911150418/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/spy|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

